Questions
1. Create a procedure that allows you to get the category of a movie, using category ID. Also add the statement to call the procedure.
2. Create a procedure that allows you to create a new category of movie. 

Answers
1
CREATE PROCEDURE Get_Category(cat_id INT)
BEGIN
SELECT * FROM category
WHERE category_id = cat_id;
END!
delimiter ;
CALL Get_Category(3);

2
delimiter !
CREATE PROCEDURE New_Category(cat_name varchar(30))
BEGIN
INSERT INTO category(name, last_update)
VALUES (cat_name, now());
END!
delimiter ;
CALL New_Category('Educational');
